### Compiling Facts

```prolog
?- go_target:compile_facts_to_go(user, 2, Code).
```

**Generated Go:**

```go
type USER struct {
    Arg1 string
    Arg2 string
}

func GetAllUSER() []USER {
    return []USER{
        {Arg1: "john", Arg2: "25"},
        {Arg1: "jane", Arg2: "30"},
    }
}

func StreamUSER(fn func(USER)) {
    for _, fact := range GetAllUSER() {
        fn(fact)
    }
}

func ContainsUSER(target USER) bool { ... }
```

